creator: James Russell Lowell; Nathan Haskell Dole
description:
LibriVox recording of Early Poems by James Russell Lowell; Nathan Haskell Dole.
Read in English by Jesse Zuba; Kane Mercer; Newgatenovelist; heeheekitty; Sarah Sellari; Guest; adamegan; Scott Bennett; Louis Keye; Ken Masters; Eliza Winters; Ezwa; Kevin Powell; Larry Wilson; Vetta; Matthew Smith; SkyAlbatross; Emily Sullivan; Domenica Campbell; shevyon4HIM; Bruce Kachuk
This is a volume of the early poems by James Russell Lowell, including a brief biographical sketch by Nathan Haskell Dole. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
